data.description: Price reduction, motivated sellers will consider accepting VA loan assumption and early occupancy offers. This 15th floor unit has gorgeous ocean, mountain, and marina views. It is move in ready and features central A/C, a private lanai, spacious bedrooms, SS appliances, full size washer and dryer, luxury vinyl and ceramic tile flooring, solid wood cabinets, fresh paint, and an exterior storage locker. The 2 covered and secured parking spots are side by side and close to the entrance. The Commodore is a PET FRIENDLY, well maintained, and secure building with maintenance fees that cover basic cable, internet, chilled water for the A/C, and hot water. Enjoy the resort like amenities which include a heated swimming pool, whirlpool, exercise room, sauna, BBQ areas, a rec room with a pool table, game room, and a library. You will love living in Hawaii Kai, tucked away in the quiet Hahaione Valley, where you will be close to world famous beaches, convenient shopping, a variety of restaurants, and top-rated schools. Come visit at our open house or make your appointment today. It's very easy to see.
